OL,3,CSpring clock change can impact
OL,4,Cinvestors response to company earnings
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FThe spring clock change significantly
OL,8,Faffects how investors respond to
OL,9,Fcompanies that reveal unexpected
OL,10,Flevels of earnings, new research shows.
OL,12,FThe study suggests that sleep
OL,13,Fdisruption resulting from the one-hour
OL,14,Fchange means financiers underreact
OL,15,Fwhen firms announce higher earnings
OL,16,Fthan analysts predicted.
