OL,3,CSpring clock change can impact
OL,4,Cinvestors response to company earnings
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FA study conducted at the University of
OL,8,FEdinburgh's business school says when
OL,9,Fa so-called earnings surprise
OL,10,Fcoincides with the spring reset, when
OL,11,Fclocks go forward an hour, an affected
OL,12,Fcompany's stock return typically
OL,13,Fdrifts towards what seems to be the
OL,14,Fcorrect valuation in the post-
OL,15,Fannouncement period.
OL,17,FResearchers say their findings are
OL,18,Fconsistent with sleep-deprived
OL,19,Finvestors mispricing and subsequently
OL,20,Frevisiting relevant information.
