OL,4,Cinvestors response to company earnings
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FThe team says its findings highlight
OL,8,Fthe vital role that investors'
OL,9,Fcognitive ability ` specifically
OL,10,Freasoning and processing speed ` plays
OL,11,Fin efficient market pricing.
OL,13,FThis study is the first to gauge how
OL,14,Fthe move to Daylight Saving Time (DST)
OL,15,Faffects the information-processing
OL,16,Fcapabilities of investors.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/8
