OL,3,CSpring clock change can impact
OL,4,Cinvestors response to company earnings
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FThe research team hopes the study `
OL,8,Fpublished in The European Journal of
OL,9,FFinance ` will deepen understanding of
OL,10,Fthe effects of sleep deprivation on
OL,11,Ffinancial markets.
OL,13,FThe team carried out its research by
OL,14,Faligning the start of DST to pricing
OL,15,Fpatterns generated by news about
OL,16,Findividual stocks ` including post-
OL,17,Fannouncement drift.
