OL,3,CSpring clock change can impact
OL,4,Cinvestors response to company earnings
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FPrevious research, by contrast, which
OL,8,Fassessed DST's impact on market-wide
OL,9,Fvolatility, did not look at individual
OL,10,Fstocks, meaning other interpretations
OL,11,Ffor pricing patterns were possible.
OL,13,FThe team studied a large sample of
OL,14,Fearnings announcements, made between
OL,15,F1993 and 2018, in the wake of the
OL,16,Fspring clocks reset.
OL,18,FThese were then contrasted with
OL,19,Fearnings forecasts made at the time.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/8
