OL,3,CSpring clock change can impact
OL,4,Cinvestors response to company earnings
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FUnexpected increases in earnings
OL,8,Fwithin the target group were then
OL,9,Fcompared with a control group of
OL,10,Fsimilar companies that had announced
OL,11,Ffinancial results exactly one week
OL,12,Fearlier.
OL,14,FThe team found that following the
OL,15,Ftransition to DST, the stock prices of
OL,16,Ffirms in the target group underreacted
OL,17,Fto earnings surprises by 36 per cent
OL,18,Frelative to control firms.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/8
