OL,4,Cinvestors response to company earnings
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FCompanies in the target group also
OL,8,Fexperienced a sizeable post-
OL,9,Fannouncement drift.
OL,11,FIn the weeks following earnings
OL,12,Fsurprises, firms in the target group
OL,13,Fexperienced returns that were about
OL,14,Ftwice the level of those experienced
OL,15,Fby firms in the control groups.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/8
