OL,3,CSpring clock change can impact
OL,4,Cinvestors response to company earnings
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FAngelica Gonzales, senior lecturer in
OL,8,Ffinance at the university, said:
OL,9,F"These high levels of returns are
OL,10,Fconsistent with investors revisiting `
OL,11,Fand reversing ` their initial
OL,12,Funderreaction to earnings surprises.
OL,14,F"Since the reversal is evident as
OL,15,Fearly as 10 days post-announcement,
OL,16,Fthis suggests the return patterns can
OL,17,Fbe explained by investors revisiting
OL,18,Fthe original earnings surprise as
OL,19,Ftheir sleep recovers ` rather than the
OL,20,Farrival of new information."
